Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈美 君島就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裏 一君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點私事要辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要好好回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去做君島拜託給我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很膽小的 你清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 要幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}抓緊心中的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}即使被絕望和失望打垮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}最後仍會站起來 獨自的Glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}不能逃避的 Battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}將足跡向下一個地點延伸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}即使把白色的地圖染成紅色也要前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}風險和不利是導火索
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,420)}將興奮的「確信」之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}射向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Reckless fire 如此大膽地 磨練生命之術
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}這個世界是生還者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}無論白與黑所走的路只有一條
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}不可能熄滅 此刻心中的篝火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}希望能貫徹堅定不移的本能與意志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(380,475,468,475,0,1600)}{\fad(1500,1000)}最 差 的 劇 本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(380,455,460,455,0,1600)}{\fad(1500,1000)}Mad·Sprict
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一級罪犯NP3228現身了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然還活著麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 那個男人在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你到底有多蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連螢火蟲也多少會考慮些的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 別那麼沖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是來這裡向你挑釁的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是幹什麼來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要加入聖堂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這笑話可不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於你的關係 到底有多少隊員被送進醫院...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的思想發生什麼轉變了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你們打過之後就充分認識到你們的強大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是順從主義者 不打無把握之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為撒這種謊有人信麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎麼樣才能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼都不會相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不明擺著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這有點頭痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摯友 友愛 愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這些都是從相信別人開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是從此開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是聖堂隊長 馬汀·吉格馬魯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NP32..啊 不 你的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一馬 是不是真名不清楚 姓氏也沒有
